.row
  section.page.small-11.large-10.small-centered.columns
    .row
        h2.columns Awesome! Your classified is now up and running!
        p.columns
          | Your classified has been successfully uploaded and
          | <% if(obj.isGuest) { %>
          | has been sent for review by our moderators.
          | <% } else { %>
          | is now online.
          | <% } %>
          | &nbsp;It will be online for 30 days after which it will automatically expire and be hidden from search results.

        | <% if(obj.isGuest) { %>
        p.columns Since you posted as a guest, you will have to use this link <a href="#" id="authLink"></a> to delete/edit your classified.
        | <% } %>
        p.columns You can help bring some attention to your classified by sharing it on your social networks.
    .row
      .columns
        ul#social-links.small-block-grid-1.medium-block-grid-3
          li
            a(href="#").facebook.social.row
              .icon.small-3.columns &#xf09a;
              .text.small-9.columns Share on Facebook
          li
            a(href="#").twitter.social.row
              .icon.small-3.columns &#xf099;
              .text.small-9.columns Tweet on Twitter
          li
            a(href="#").gplus.social.row
              .icon.small-3.columns &#xf0d5;
              .text.small-9.columns Share on Google+
          li
            .button.submit.small-12
              a#finishLink(href="", data-view) View your classified

    .seperator
    .row#shared-message

      h3.columns Your classified is promoted!
      p.columns Thanks so much for spreading the love! We have promoted your classified as a token of our apprecition :)
    .row#unshared-message
      h3.columns Promote with a share!
      p.columns
        | We love doing beautiful things for you! Show us some love back and we
        | will return the favour by <b>promoting your classified onto the
        | front-page</b> and on top of search results.
      p.columns
        | All you have to do is simply share the site in your social network by
        | clicking on the button below

      .columns.medium-4.end
        .button.submit#promoteLink Promote with a share